&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen to join the Endoscopy Admin Team at Worcestershire Acute Hospitals NHS Trust&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are seeking an enthusiastic individual to join our friendly well established team. The job role requires a friendly, welcoming individual who will work front of house, greeting patients on arrival to the Endoscopy departments.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Excellent communication, customer care and IT skills are essential. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Previous experience of working in the NHS in an administrative role would be desirable but is not fundamental.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There is a requirement to travel between Worcestershire Acute Hospital sites as necessary; The Worcestershire Royal Hospital, The Kidderminster Treatment Centre &amp; The Alexandra Hospital, Redditch.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further details, please contact Sarah Bailey on 01905 763333 ext. 30280 or Louise Burgess on 01562 826328 or ext. 53359&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
